551
00:42:51,660 --> 00:42:53,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah mertuaku mencarimu.</font>

552
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:56,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mungkin melapor ke polisi dan
