553
00:43:03,660 --> 00:43:04,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini saya.</font>

554
00:43:05,550 --> 00:43:07,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan panggil polisi atau apapun.</font>

555
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:11,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari bertemu langsung.</font>

556
00:43:14,530 --> 00:43:15,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

557
00:43:15,750 --> 00:43:17,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi dengan aksen bicaranya?</font>

558
00:43:30,300 --> 00:43:31,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau?</font>

559
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:32,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Nyonya.</font>

560
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:34,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

561
00:43:34,270 --> 00:43:35,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mungkin saja membunuhmu!</font>

562
00:43:36,350 --> 00:43:40,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya melihat seorang pria yang menginap
